             <lg> 
              <l>i point to the field of yellow outside</l>
          <l>sunflowers worship the sun i tell him</l> 
          <l>only when it arrives do they rise</l>
          <l>when the sun leaves</l>
          <l>they bow their heads in mourning</l>
          <l>that is what the sun does to those flowers</l>
          <l>it's what you do to me</l>
        <l>           rupi kaur</l> 
